President Joe Biden has announced the designation of a Presidential Delegation to attend the inauguration of Ferdinand Romualdez Marcos Jr. in the Philippines on June 30, 2022. The delegation will be led by Douglas Emhoff, the Second Gentleman of the United States. Other members of the delegation include Heather Variava, Bobby Scott, Nani A. Coloretti, Admiral James "Sandy" A. Winnefeld Jr., Edgard D. Kagan, and Chantale Y. Wong.